extendedInfo.description: Starry night is a beautiful live wallpaper of a peaceful scene overlooking a dazzling starry night sky, with the occasional shooting star! If you enjoy this live wallpaper, please buy Starry night Pro. It has a full settings screen with lots of customization options to choose from!TO USE: Menu -> Wallpaper -> Live Wallpaper -> Starry night LitePro Version: http://market.android.com/details?id=com.dmfsoftware.starrynight.pro~>Android 2.1+Your phone must support live wallpapers for Num clock to work. Go to: Menu -> Wallpaper, if you see the option "Live Wallpapers" your phone supports it.~>Not optimized for tabletsPlease contact me by email with any feedback on issues you may encounter, or with suggestions on how to improve Starry night!To see updates about my current android projects and new ones visit my blog at http://davidfahr.com/?page_id=128 to stay up to date! ___{o,o}/)__)-â-â-Keywords: live wallpaper, lwp, animation, stars, sky, night, shooting star, customize, abstract, lite, pro
